r2t2pnsh0Ty is a player spoof that can occasionally be found in the second level of the Hallowed Sepulchre.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Her name is a reference to a meme which calls a gun "rooty tooty point and shooty".
  • Her examine text is most likely a reference to the fact that outside of combat, most players look identical as they tend to wear the full graceful outfit for efficiency, therefore she, or other players that look like her, have most likely been seen before.
